---
import '../styles/styles.scss';
---
<div class="label label-mac-n-cheese">
  <header>
    <h1 class="bold">Nutrition Facts</h1>
    <h3 class="bold">(Kraft Mac 'n' Cheese)</h3>
    <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese"></div>
    <p>About 3 servings per container</p>
    <p class="bold">Serving size <span>2.5 oz<br>(70g/ about 1/3 box)</span></p>
    <p class="bold">&#8203;<span>(Makes about 1 cup)</span></p>
  </header>
  <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese large"></div>
  <div class="calories-info">
    <div class="left-container">
      <h2 class="bold small-text">Amount per 1 cup prepared</h2>
      <p>Calories</p>
    </div>
    <span>350</span>
  </div>
  <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese medium"></div>
  <div class="wen-xin-ti-xing">
    <p class="bold">百佳免運費: <span>精選貨品買滿$800 - 92折</span></p>
  </div>
  <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese medium"></div>
  <div class="daily-value small-text">
    <p class="bold right no-divider">% Daily Value *</p>
    <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese"></div>
    <p>
      <span><span class="bold">Total Fat</span> 11g</span>
      <span class="bold">15%</span>
    </p>
    <p class="indent no-divider">
      Saturated Fat 4g <span class="bold">19%</span>
    </p>
    <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese"></div>
    <p class="indent no-divider"><span><i>Trans</i> Fat 0g</span></p>
    <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese"></div>
    <p>
      <span>
        <span class="bold">Cholesterol</span> 10mg</span>
      </span>
      <span class="bold">3%</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span><span class="bold">Sodium</span> 710mg</span>
      <span class="bold">31%</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span><span class="bold">Total Carb.</span> 50g</span>
      <span class="bold">18%</span>
    </p>
    <p class="indent no-divider">
      <span>Dietary Fiber 2g</span>
      <span>8%</span>
    </p>
    <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese"></div>
    <p class="indent no-divider">Total Sugars 10g</p>
    <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese double-indent"></div>
    <p class="double-indent no-divider">
      Incl. Added Sugars 0g<span class="bold">0%</span>
      <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese"></div>
    </p>
    <p class="no-divider"><span class="bold">Protein</span> 10g
      <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese large"></div>
      <p>Vitamin D 0mg <span>0%</span></p>
      <p>Calcium 130mg <span>10%</span></p>
      <p>Iron 2.5mg <span>15%</span></p>
      <p class="no-divider">Potassium 370mg <span>8%</span></p>
    </p>
    <div class="divider devider-mac-n-cheese medium"></div>
    <p class="note no-divider">
      * As prepared using margarine with 0g trans fat and 2% reduced fat milk.
    </p>
    <p class="note no-divider">
      * The % Daily Value (DV) tells you how much a nutrient in a serving of
      food contributes to a daily diet. 2,000 calories a day is used for
      general nutrition advice.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>